    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and truly stands out as a collector-quality example. The exterior paint retains its original showroom luster with no scratches, dents, or chips, while the interior is pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained with a full service history. Buyers can expect a car that looks and drives as if it were brand new.",
