    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this stunning vehicle in absolute mint condition! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, featuring a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that has been meticulously maintained. This is a rare find for any driver seeking a truly like-new experience with top-tier performance and elegance.",
